PombePD - Model organism S. pombe .WormPD - Model organism C. elegans .MycoPathPD - Human fungal pathogen DB .A biochemical pathways database searchable by keyword or partial word .When a match is found , you will be given a list of all matching entries of the Biochemical Pathways index of Boehringer Mannheim , with links to all maps of Biochemical Pathways in which the entry appears .
